i'm glad he's out of my life. and that makes me sad. i read his LJ today, something about some little afghani kid made fun of him, and now he wants to kill this kid. what the fuck? if i wasn;t certain before, i'm certain now - this is not the danny i loved. 

i no longer feel bad about not missing him, because he's nothing worth missing. the danny i loved was worth missing, but that one's gone forever. ah well. i suppose that's all for Melani's Deep Dark Thoughts No One Should Know About But The Closest Of Friends.




see you, space cowboy....
